cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM 

This paper deals with image super resolution using GANs and local saliency maps, which are techniques commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.AI). The use of GANs also falls under the category of deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with retinal vasculature segmentation, which is a topic in graphics (cs.GR) and medical imaging (cs.MM).
